price: Entonces el Faraón se retiró y se dedicó a reclutar hechiceros. Luego, el día de la cita, concurrió.
arabic: فَتَوَلَّىٰ فِرۡعَوۡنُ فَجَمَعَ كَيۡدَهُۥ ثُمَّ أَتَىٰ

version.title: Spanish Translation - Isa Garcia
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Spanish by Muhammad Isa Garcia - Printed in 1433 H.

meta.transliteration: fatawallā fir'ʿawnu fajamaʿa kaydahu thumma atā
